<section class="tool-header">
  <%= render partial: 'pages/shared/home_navbar' %>
  <% @active_tab = 'Quill Grammar' %>
  <%= render partial: "pages/shared/tools_tabs", active_tab: @active_tab %>
</section>
<div class="tool-container">

    <section class='bg-purple bg-image-grammar-pattern tool-hero text-center'>
      <h1 class="q-h1">
        Quill Grammar
      </h1>
      <p class='description'>
        Quill Grammar has over 150 sentence writing activities to help your students practice basic grammar skills, from comma placement to parallel structure. Our activities are designed to be completed in 10 minutes so you have the freedom to use them in the way that works best for your classroom.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="tool-animation-section ">
          <video class='tool-animation' src="/videos/grammar.mp4" autoplay loop/>
    </section>

  <section class="tool-carousel">
      <div id="diagnosticCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">

          <a class="left carousel-control" href="#diagnosticCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
          </a>

          <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
          <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
              <div class="item active">
                <div class="wrapper">
                  <img src="/images/tools/Grammar1.png" alt="Chania">
                </div>
                <p>Students are tasked with writing a complete sentence by incorporating proper grammar, punctuation, and spelling.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <div class="wrapper">
                  <img src="/images/tools/Grammar2.png" alt="Chania">
                </div>
                <p>Students receive instant feedback on the quality of their writing.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <div class="wrapper">
                  <img src="/images/tools/Grammar3.png" alt="Flower">
                </div>
                <p>Students are provided with an opportunity to try again if they make a mistake. If, on the 2nd attempt, a students do not write a complete sentence, the program shows the students where the studentâ€™s error is.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <div class="wrapper">
                  <img src="/images/tools/Grammar4.png" alt="Flower">
                </div>
                <p>Teachers access in-depth reports that show them how the students have performed on all of the materials over the course of the year.</p>
              </div>

              <div class="item">
                <div class="wrapper">
                  <img src="/images/tools/Grammar5.png" alt="Flower">
                </div>
                <p>Teachers have access to over 200 exercises aligned with the Common Core language standards.</p>
              </div>

          </div>

          <!-- Left and right controls -->

          <a class="right carousel-control" href="#diagnosticCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
          </a>

          <!-- Indicators -->
          <ol class="carousel-indicators">
              <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
              <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
              <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
              <li data-target="#diagnosticCarousel" data-slide-to="3"></li>
          </ol>

      </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tool-try-it bg-purple bg-image-grammar-pattern">
    <h2 class='q-h1'>Try It Yourself!</h2>
    <a href='/activity_sessions/anonymous?activity_id=110' class="q-button cta-button bg-white text-purple">Sign Up</a>
  </section>

  <section class="tool-testimonial">
    <p class='quote'>
      "Using Quill has opened up more conversations between me and my students, in terms of how to write better and what the student needs to practice."
    </p>
    <h4 class="q-h4 author">
      MADISON VALDEZ, 8TH GRADE ELA EDUCATOR
    </h4>
    <a href="/" class='q-button text-black'>
      <span>View My Story</span>
    </a>
  </section>

<!-- Only how if user is not logged in  -->
  <%if !current_user%>
    <section class="tool-sign-up">
        <h1 class='q-h1'>
            Sign up to start using Quill Grammar in your class today!
        </h1>
        <a href='/account/new' class="q-button cta-button bg-quillgreen text-white">Sign Up</a>
    </section>
  <%end%>

</div>

<%= render partial: 'pages/shared/footer' %>
